               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 2ra l.1–53rb
                     l.10)&#xD; - Homily of St Jacob of Serug on funeral of priests and deacons
                     (fols. 11rb l.3–15rb l.6)&#xD; - Homily of ʾAbbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of
                     Ethiopia (fols. 32rb l.10–35rb l.10)&#xD; II) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the
                     Christening”, called here Maṣḥafa ṭǝmqat (fols. 54ra l.1–71rb l.8). For the
                     title of the book s. e.g., EMML 3107 (EMML VIII, 94)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
